\id 1TI - rough draft by Berama Oct 2000; exeg ck June 2002 in village: comp ck July 2002; consultant ck by M Sweeney in Madang Jan 03; revisons by Francis and Marsha Aug 03; ready for publication. Published with 2004 Aruamu NT. Revised by Aruamu translation team in 2019-2020, with input from many Aruamus.
\h 1 Timoti
\toc3 1TI
\toc2 1 Timoti
\toc1 Ak…®nafarir Faragha Zuim, Pol Timoti Baghava an Osiri
\mt1 Ak…®nafarir Faragha Zuim, // Pol Timoti Baghava an Osiri
\mt2 O
\mt1 1 Timoti
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Timoti, Krais…®n adarazir gumazir igiar mam, a Listran nguibar ekiar Galesian Provinis…®n itim…®n ize. An amebam, a Judan amizim, ez…® an afeziam a Grigh…®n gumazim. Pol Timoti iniz…®ma, an a koma aruava God…®n ingangarim gami. (N…® Aposel 16:1-3…®n gan.) Ez…® Timoti g…®n Efesus…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itir sios…®n gumazir dapanim…®n oto. Ez…® Pol ak…®nafarir kam a bagha an osiri.
\ip Ak…®nafarim faragha m…®geir bizim, a kamak…®n, Timoti derav…®ra ua bagh ganigh, gumazitaba gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibagh as…®ghasighan maraghe. Gumazir kaba, me n…®ghn…®zir igharaziba ikia ghaze, nguazir kam…®n itir biziba, da derazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazim guizbang…®n ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim inis…®va, dagher taba ategh…®va egh amuim…®n ikian mark…®.
\ip Bizir igharazir ekiar ak…®nafarim m…®geir mam, Timoti sios…®n ingangarim derav…®ram an ganam. Egha a uaghan m…®g…®a ghaze, sios…®n gumazamizir dapaniba ko sios…®n ingangarir gumazamiziba, me arazir aghuibar amu.
\ip Ak…®nafarim…®n akar abuananaba, Pol Timoti m…®g…®a ghaze, a Krais Iesus…®n ingangarir gumazir aghuimra ik…®, egh arazir aghuibar vaghvagh sios…®n gumazamizibar amu.
\c 1
\ms1 Timoti uab…® uan araziba deraghv…®ra dar gan, egh sios…®n gumazamiziba uaghan men gan
\mr (Sapta 1--6)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Kolosi 1:27\x*K…® Pol, k…® Krais Iesus…®n aposel. God, en Akurvazir Gumazim, ko Krais Iesus, gumazir e ganasa m…®zuaim, aning na m…®sevez…®ma k…® aposel…®n oto.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Aposel 16:1; Taitus 1:4\x*Timoti, n…® na ko n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikiava, mati guizbang…®ra nan otarim. Ez…® k…® ak…®nafarir kam n…® bagha an osiri. God en Afeziam ko Krais Iesus en Ekiam, aning…®n apangkuvim ko kuarkuvim, n…® damut…® n…® navir am…®rizim…®n ik…®.
\s1 E ifavarir akaba bar a da baraghan kogham
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Galesia 1:6; Filipai 2:24\x*K…® fom…®ra Masedonian Provins…®n ghughava, dughiar kam…®n k…® akar gavgavir mam n…® gan…®ngi, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® akar kamra ua kamagh…®n n…® m…®k…®masa. K…® ghaze, n…® Efesus…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n ik…®va gumazir maba m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim me dan…®ng suam, me gumazamiziba God…®n akam…®n men sure damuva, akar ifavarir taba me damuv…®ra ikian mark…®.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 1 Timoti 4:7; 2 Timoti 2:14-16; Taitus 1:14\x*Egh me pura eghaghanir araziba ko men ovavibar ziar m…®g…®r…®g…®ar me zurara m…®g…®av…®ra itiba, da atakigh. Akar kaba men n…®ghn…®zibagh amima me onganighava tintinibar uariv g…®a uari adosi. Akar kaba me damut…®, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikian kogham, egh God e damuamin bizim me deragh a g…®foghan kogham.
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Rom 13:8-10; Galesia 5:14; 2 Timoti 2:22\x*Nan akar gavgavir kam…®n m…®ngarimra kara, e bar uarigh ifuegham. E fo, e guiz…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ikia, navir zuruzim ikia, egha uan araziba derav…®ra da tuis…®gha arazir aghuibar g…®n zui. Eght…® bizir kaba e damut…®, e bar uarigh ifuegham.
\v 6 Marazi arazir kam ataki, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n me onganigha pura akar m…®ngariba puvat…®zibav gei.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt 1 Timoti 6:4; 6:20; Taitus 1:10\x*Egha me igharaz darazi God…®n Arazibar men sure damuasa. Egha me ghaze, men m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bar guizbang…®ra. Ez…® akar me gun m…®geim, an m…®ngarim me uari a g…®fozir puvat…®, egha me uari uan akam deragha a g…®fozir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Rom 7:12; 7:16; 7:22\x*E kamagh…®n fo, Moses Osirizir Arazir God a Gan…®ngiziba, da bar dera. Eght…® gumazitam bar deragh God…®n Arazir kabar g…®n mang…®t…®, Arazir Kaba an deragham.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Galesia 3:19; 5:23\x*Ez…® e uaghan kamagh…®n fo, God uan Araziba isa gumazamizir aghuiba bagha da an…®ngizir pu. Puvat…®, a gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amiba bagha, da me gan…®ngi. Gumazamizir akaba batoziba, ko akaba barazir puvat…®ziba, ko gumazir ak…®rim ragha God gasaraziba, merara God me bagha uan Araziba an…®ngi. Kar gumazamizir God…®n ziam fer puvat…®ziba, ko gumazamizir God…®n aghuaziba, ko gumazamizir uan amebaba ko afeziaba m…®soghez…® me aremeziba, ko gumazamizir igharaz darazi m…®sozima me ariaghireziba,
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Jenesis 19:4-5; 1 Timoti 6:3; 2 Timoti 4:3; Taitus 1:9\x*ko arazir m…®z…®r…®zibagh amiba, ko gumazir uarira uari isava akuiba, ko gumazir gumazamiziba ok…®ava me gamima me pura ingangarir gumazamizibar otiviba, ko gumazamizir ifariba, ko gumazamizir kot…®n aven ifariba, merara God me bagha uan Araziba an…®ngi. Egha uaghan gumazamizir God…®n guiz…®n akam…®n apaniba, God me bagha uan Araziba an…®ngi.
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Galesia 2:7; Kolosi 1:25; 1 Tesalonika 2:4; 1 Timoti 6:15\x*Ez…® guiz…®n akar kam, God an gun m…®k…®masa na gan…®ngizir akam, an Akar Aghuir kam…®n m…®rara ghu. Ez…® Akar Aghuir kam e m…®g…®a ghaze, God angazangarir ekiam…®n aven ikia, egha gavgavir ekiam iti. A bar deraz…®ma gumazamiziba an ziam fe.
\s1 God Pol…®n apangkuviz…®ma, Pol a m…®nabi
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Aposel 9:15; Galesia 1:15-16\x*En Ekiam Krais Iesus, ingangarim bagha gavgavim na ganigha ghaze, k…® an ingangarim damuam. Egha ingangarir kam damuasa na am…®sefe. Ez…® k…® kamaghsua a m…®naba.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Aposel 3:17; 8:3; 9:4-5; 1 Korin 15:9-10; Galesia 1:13\x*Guizbang…®ra, fom…®ra k…® d…®bovir akabar an ziam gas…®ghas…®ki, egha an apanim gamuava, akar kurabar a m…®keme. Ez…® a fo, k…® deragha a g…®fozir puvat…®gha, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®, egha arazir kabagh ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, a nan apangkufi.
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Luk 7:47; Rom 5:20; 1 Korin 15:10; 2 Timoti 1:13\x*Ez…® Krais Iesus en Ekiam…®n apangkuvim bar na giz…®vagha, na gamima, k…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikiava gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais Iesus…®n itiba, bar me gifonge.
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Luk 15:2; 19:10; Rom 5:8; 1 Timoti 3:1; 4:9; 2 Timoti 2:11; 1 Jon 3:5\x*Krais Iesus, gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amiba men akuraghasa nguazir kam…®n ize. Ez…® men tong…®n, nan arazir kuraba bar men arazir kurabagh afira. Ez…® akar kam a guizbang…®ra, gumazamiziba a baregh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ik…®.
\v 16 Ez…® Krais Iesus kamaghsua ifonge, gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n fogh, a gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amibar asughasugha n…®m…®ra me gamua zui. Kamagh amiz…® a faragha nan apangkufi, ez…® k…® an ababanim…®n m…®n iti, eght…® a na gamizir biziba men akaght…® me dar gan…®va, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ik…®va, ik…®r…®m…®rir ikia mamagh…®ra itim iniam.
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Daniel 7:14; Jon 1:18; Rom 16:27; Hibru 11:27; 1 Jon 4:12\x*Ez…® an Atrivir Zurara Itim. An oveghan kogham, ez…® e gumazamiziba an ganighan kogham. A uab…®ra bar guizbang…®n God. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e zurazurara ziar ekiam a dan…®ng mamagh…®ra ik…® m…®k…®m suam, God n…® bar ekevegha bar dera. Bar guizbang…®ra.
\s1 Pol Timoti m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir Iesus…®n itim, an suiragh gavgafigh
\p 
\v 18-19 \x - \xo 1:18-19 \xt 1 Timoti 3:9; 6:9; 6:12; Jut 1:3\x*Nan otarim Timoti, k…® fo, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim fom…®ra n…®n arazibar gun m…®keme. Ez…® k…® akar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha, bizir n…® damuamiba bar dar gun n…® m…®gei. K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ik…®va an suiragh gavgavigh, uan araziba derav…®ra da tuis…®gh arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®. K…® kamaghsua, n…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim n…® gan…®ngizir akar kabar g…®n mang…®, egh tuavir kam…®n n…® m…®dorozir aghuim m…®sogh…®va n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n aven tugh gavgafigh. Bizir kam bagha, k…® akar kam n…® gan…®di. Ez…® gumazir maba, me uan araziba deragha da tuis…®gha, arazir aghuibar g…®n mangan aghuagha da batosi. Egha tuavir kam…®n me uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibagh as…®ghas…®ki.
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt 1 Korin 5:5; 2 Timoti 2:17-18; 4:14-15\x*Ez…® men tong…®n Himeneus ko Aleksander kamagh…®n ami. Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n ifonge, aning ua God…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®ghan markiam. Aning kamagh…®n foghasa, k…® aning isa Satan…®n agharim gat…®.
\c 2
\s1 E gumazamizibar akurvaghs…® God ko m…®k…®m…®va an azangs…®gham
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1-2 \xt Jeremaia 29:7; Esekiel 6:10; Rom 13:1; Efesus 6:18; Filipai 4:6\x*K…® m…®gh…®ghav…®ra ia m…®gei, faragh damuamin bizim a kamak…®n, ia gumazamiziba bagh God ko m…®k…®m…®va a m…®nab…®va an azangs…®gh…®va, egh a gumazamiziba bar men akurvaghs…® a gakaghon.
\v 2 Egh uaghan atriviba ko gavmanba bagh God…®n azangs…®gh. Kamagh…®n, e bar deragh ik…®va navir am…®rizibar ik…®va, God baghav…®ra itir arazibar amuva, God ifongezir araziba bar dar g…®n mangam.
\v 3 God ko m…®geir arazir kam, a God…®n damazim…®n bar dera. God, en Akurvazir Gumazim, an arazir kam gifonge.
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Esekiel 18:23; Jon 3:16-17; 17:3; 1 Timoti 4:10; 2 Timoti 2:25; 2 Pita 3:9\x*A kamaghsua, a bar gumazamiziba men akurvagham. Eght…® me bar guiz…®n akam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fogham.
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Rom 3:29-30; Galesia 3:20; Hibru 8:6; 9:15; 12:24\x*E fo, God…®n vam…®ra iti. Ez…® abuir gumazir vam…®ra iti, a God ko en tigh…®n iti. A gumazir kamra, Krais Iesus.
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Matyu 20:28; 1 Korin 1:6; Galesia 1:4; Efesus 1:7-9; 2 Tesalonika 1:10; Taitus 1:3\x*Dughiar God inabazim…®n, Krais Iesus gumazamiziba bar me bagha uab…® isa God ganigha aremegha ua me givese. Ez…® arazir kam…®n God kamagh…®n en aka, a uan gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra ua me iniam.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Aposel 9:15; Galesia 1:16; 2:7-8; Efesus 3:7-8; 2 Timoti 1:11\x*Egha ingangarir kam bagha, God aposel ko akam akunamin gumazim…®n ikiasa na m…®sefe. K…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, k…® ifarir puvat…®. A Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar sure damuasa ingangarim na gan…®ngi, eght…® me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n ik…®va guiz…®n akam g…®fogham.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Aisaia 1:15; Malakai 1:11; Jon 4:21\x*K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, nguazir kam…®n gumaziba bar dafariba f…®va God ko m…®k…®m. K…® kamaghsua, me bar uari is…®va God dan…®ng…®va, zuegh ik…®va, an…®ngagharir arazim ko adoghodozir arazim atakigh. Me arazir kam damuva, God ko m…®k…®m.
\s1 Ingangarir aghuim damuamin arazim, a guiz…®n amizibar kurukazim
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1 Pita 3:3-5\x*K…® uaghan kamagh…®n ifonge, amiziba korotiar aghuibar aghut…®, da men tughat…®gham. Eght…® men korotiaba, igharaz darazi men gan…®va n…®ghn…®zir kuraba ko aghums…®zir n…®ghn…®ziba ikian kogham. Me uan dapanir ar…®ziba m…®ghv…®ra da as…®ngan mark…®, egh uan m…®karziba, manmaniaba ko gol ko korotiar bar p…®n koziba, puram azenan dar kurukan mark…®.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt 1 Timoti 5:10\x*Amizir God…®n akam…®n g…®n mangasa ifongeziba, me arazir aghuibar amu. Arazir kaba, kar guiz…®n men kurukazim.
\p 
\v 11 Egh amizir mam bar uab…® d…®kab…®ragh n…®m…®ra ik…®va God…®n akam…®n fofozim iniam.
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt 1 Korin 14:34\x*K…® kamagh…®n amizir kam…®n amamangat…®zir puvat…®, a uab…® f…®va gumazim…®n faraghfaragh mang…®, egh an sure damuan kogham. Amizir kam n…®m…®ra ik…®.
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Jenesis 2:7; 2:21-22; 1 Korin 11:8-9\x*Ia oragh! God faragha Adam…®n ingarigha, g…®n Iv…®n ingari.
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Jenesis 3:1-6; 2 Korin 11:3\x*Ez…® Adam akar ifavariba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim a dar itir puvat…®. Amizimra akar ifavariba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim a dar iti, egha arazir kuram gami.
\v 15 Amizim boriba batir ingangarim damuva, egh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim zurara Krais…®n ik…®va uab…® is…®va a dan…®ng…®va zuegh ik…®, egh a igharaz darazigh ifongegh, arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®t…®, God an akuragham.\f + \fr 2:15 \ft Grigh…®n akam, vez…®n kam…®n deragha bigha m…®kemezir puvat…®.\f*
\c 3
\s1 Sios…®n gumazamizir dapaniba arazir aghuibar amu
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Aposel 20:28; Efesus 4:12; Filipai 1:1; 1 Timoti 1:15\x*Akar kam a bar guizbang…®ra, tina sios…®n dapanir mam…®n ik…®s…® a ingangarir aghuim gifonge.
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt 1 Timoti 5:9; 2 Timoti 2:24\x*\x - \xo 3:2-7 \xt Taitus 1:6-9\x*Sios…®n dapanim, an arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®, eght…® me arazir kuratam bagh an gan…®va avegham. An amuir vam…®ra ik…®, egh poroghamir arazim ab…®ghan mark…®. Egh an dabirabim bar mogh…®ra deragh, navir ghurim…®n araziba d…®kab…®ragh, egh arazir aghuibara damu ziar aghuim iniva, gumazamizir igharaziba ini d…®penim…®n mang…®va, derav…®ra gumazamizibar sure damu.
\v 3 A wain…®n d…®par av…®ribar am…®va onganan mark…®. A zuam…®ra an…®ngagh…®va gumazibav soghan kogham, a men asughasugh. Egh biziba bagh gumazamiziba adoghan mark…®, egh a dag…®aba baghv…®ra ikian mark…®.
\v 4 Egh derav…®ra uan d…®penim…®n itir darazi men gan…®va, boribav k…®mt…®ma me derav…®ra an akaba baragh dar g…®n mang…®.
\v 5 Sios…®n gumazamizir dapaniba, me uan d…®penibar itir darasi deraghv…®ra men ganan kogh, manmagh…®n me God…®n sios…®n ganamin ingangarim iniam? Bar puvat…®.
\v 6 Gumazamizir dat…®r…®gh…®ra n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itiba, me God…®n sios…®n ganan kogham. Me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, e gumazamizir aghuiba, egh uan ziaba fam. Eght…® God ivezir kuram Satan gan…®ngiz…® mogh…®n ivezir kuram me dan…®ngam.
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt 1 Korin 5:12; 2 Korin 8:21; 1 Tesalonika 4:12; 1 Timoti 6:9\x*Sios…®n gumazamizir dapaniba, sios…®n azenan itir gumazamiziba me m…®k…®m suam, me ziar aghuim iti. Me ziar aghuim ikian koght…®ma, gumazamiziba akar kurabar me m…®k…®mt…®, me aghums…®gh…®va, Satan…®n azuazim…®n aven mang…®gham.
\s1 Sios…®n ingangarir gumazamiziba arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®
\p 
\v 8 Kamagh…®ra sios…®n ingangarir gumaziba, gumazibar damazibar me ziar aghuim ik…®. Egh me m…®zer pumuning…®n ikian mark…®, egh wain…®n d…®par av…®ribar am…®va onganan mark…®. Egh dag…®aba bagh bar ikuvigh ifar da inian mark…®.
\v 9 Me uan araziba deraghv…®ra da tuis…®gh arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®, egh guiz…®n akar e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itim…®n suiragh gavgafigh.
\v 10 Ia faragh me is…® ingangaritam dat…®gh ganigh. Eght…® men ingangarim deraght…®, me sios…®n ingangarir gumazibar ikiam.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Taitus 2:3\x*Kamagh…®ra, sios…®n ingangarir amiziba uaghan, gumazamizibar damazibar me ziar aghuim ik…®. Egh me igharaz darazi g…®rak…®rang…®n me m…®k…®man mark…®. Egh men dabirabim bar mogh…®ra deragh, egh me guiz…®n deraghv…®ra ingangarir me inizibar amu.
\p 
\v 12 Egh sios…®n ingangarir gumazamiziba, me poroghamir arazim ab…®ghan mark…®. Egh me uan boriba ko men d…®penibar itir darazi deragh men gan.
\v 13 Gumazamizir derav…®ra ingariba, me ziar aghuiba iniam. Egh me atiatingan kogh uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir Krais Iesus…®n itim…®n gun m…®k…®mam.
\s1 God…®n Arazibar akar mogomem, a bizir bar ekiam
\p 
\v 14 K…® gurumra iz…® ian ganasa ifonge, egha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam ia bagha an osiri.
\v 15 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® zuam…®ra izeghan koght…®, ia m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kabar gan…®va ia arazir aghuibagh fogham, arazir e God…®n adarazi damuamiba. E God…®n adarasi, e God…®n zurara itim…®n sios. Egha sios…®n aven itir darasi, erara, e d…®penir ak…®nibar m…®n gavgavigh guiz…®n akam gupugh…®va tugh gavgavigham.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Mak 16:19; Jon 1:14; 16:8-9; 1 Pita 1:12; 3:18\x*E guizbang…®ra fo, God…®n Arazibar akar mogomem, a bar bizir ekiam. Ez…® akar God en akazir kam, a kamak…®n:
\b
\q1 A guiz…®n gumazim…®n oto,
\q2 ez…® gumazamiziba an gani.
\q1 Ez…® God…®n Duam kamagh…®n en aka,
\q2 an araziba bar dera,
\q3 Ez…® enselba an gani.
\q1 Ez…® gumaziba ghua
\q2 an akam…®n gun bar gumazibav k…®ri.
\q1 Ez…® nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba
\q2 n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti.
\q1 Ez…® God a inigha uan Nguibam…®n ghuavanaboz…®
\q2 a ziar ekiam ini.
\c 4
\s1 Akar ifavariba God…®n gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zibagh as…®ghas…®si
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt 2 Timoti 3:1; 1 Pita 1:20; 2 Pita 2:1; 3:3; 1 Jon 2:18; Jut 1:18; Akar Mogomem 9:20; 16:14\x*God…®n Duam guizbang…®ra kamagh…®n m…®gei, Dughiar G…®n Izamim, gumazamizitaba uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba ategham. Egh me ifavarir duaba ko duar kurabar akaba baragh dar g…®n mangam.
\v 2 Eght…® ifavarir gumaziba, me akar ifavaribar gumazamizibar sure damuam. Men arazir aghuibar g…®n mangamin n…®ghn…®ziba ariaghire mati avim dar isiz…®, me ua uan arazir aghuiba ko kurabagh fozir puvat…®.
\v 3 \x - \xo 4:3 \xt Jenesis 9:3; Rom 14:6; 1 Korin 8:8; 10:30-31; Kolosi 2:20-21; Hibru 13:4\x*Me gumaziba amuiba ikian men anogoroke. Egha dagher God e bagha ingarizir maba, me ghaze ia dar aman mark…®. Dagher kaba, God ghaze, gumazamizir guiz…®n akam g…®fogha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itiba, merara dagher kaba iniam. Me dagheba iniva dar am…®va God m…®nabagh.
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt Jenesis 1:31; Aposel 10:15; Rom 14:14; 14:20; 1 Korin 10:25; Taitus 1:15\x*E fo, God ingarizir biziba bar, da bar dera. Ez…® e bizir kurabar m…®n a dar ganan kogham. Puvat…®. E God m…®nabagh da iniam.
