\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt 1 Korin 16:11; Taitus 2:7; 2:15; 1 Pita 5:3\x*Marazi n…®n gara ghaze, n…® gumazir igiam. Egh gumazitam kamagh…®n n…® m…®k…®man markiam, kar gumazir k…®nim. Eght…® n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itiba bagh ababanim…®n uab…® at…®gh. Egh arazir aghuibar amut…®, me n…®n arazibar gan…®va, n…®n g…®n mangam. N…®n arazir aghuibara kara: n…®n akar aghuiba, ko n…®n daroriba, ko n…®n arazir igharaz darazigh ifongezim, ko n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n arazim, ko God…®n damazim…®n zuegha itir arazim.
