\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt Ofa Gami 19:32\x*N…® gumazir aruabar atar pamten me m…®k…®man mark…®. Puvat…®, n…® uan afeziam…®n m…®n aghumra me m…®k…®m…®va me f…®. Egh gumazir igiaba, n…® uan aveghbuabagh ami mogh…®n, deragh me damu.
\v 2 Egh amizir aruaba, n…® uan amebam gami mogh…®n, arazir kamra deragh me damu. Egh amizir igiaba, n…® uan buaramizibagh ami mogh…®n, deragh me damu. Kar arazir bar God…®n damazim…®n zuezim.
\s1 Tina amizir odiaribar ganam?
