\v 3 Eght…® amizir odiaritam bar uab…®ra ik…®t…®ma, n…® bar arazir aghuim…®n a damu.
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt Matyu 15:4; Efesus 6:1-2; 1 Timoti 2:3\x*Eght…® amizir kam boriba ko igiaba ik…®t…®, n…® borir kabar akurvaght…®, me deraghv…®ra kamagh…®n fogh suam, men ingangarir faragh God…®n damazim…®n damuamim a kara, me bar deraghv…®ra uan amebam…®n ganam. Egh arazir kam…®n, me uan amebam ko afeziam…®n akurvazim ko ingangarir dafar aning fom…®ra me gamiziba ikarvagham. God arazir kam bar a gifonge.
