\v 8 \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Aisaia 58:7; Matyu 18:17; Galesia 6:10; Taitus 1:16\x*N…® oragh. Tina uan anababar ganan kogh, egh uaghan uan adarazir ganan kogh…®va, a guizbang…®ra uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ataki. An arazir kurar kam, a gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim puvat…®ziba, men arazir kurabagh afira.
