\v 13 \x - \xo 5:13 \xt 2 Tesalonika 3:11\x*Egha arazir mam me uaghan a gami. Me am…®rizir arazim gamuava pura d…®penibagh arui. Me am…®rvazir arazimra amir puvat…®, me gumazamiziba amir arazibar akaba baragha dagh ifongegha, aruava g…®rak…®rang…®n me m…®gei. Me uaghan akar e m…®k…®man koghamibav gei.
