\v 1 \x - \xo 6:1 \xt Rom 2:24; Efesus 6:5; Kolosi 3:22; Taitus 2:5; 2:8-9; 1 Pita 2:18\x*Gumazamizir igharazibar apengan itir ingangarir gumazamiziba, me bar uan gumazamizir ekiar men gariba deragh me damuva, ziar ekiaba me dan…®ng…®va men apengan ik…®. Eght…® gumazamizir ekiar men gariba, God…®n ziam ko en suren m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, akar kurabar dav k…®man kogham.
